Mercuria, China Datang Sign Clean Energy, Carbon Joint Venture

-- B y   M a t h e w   C a r r
-- 
2011-08-24T14:43:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-24/mercuria-china-datang-sign-clean-energy-carbon-joint-venture.html
Mercuria Energy Asia Investment PTE
Ltd. and China Datang Corp. Renewable Power Co. formed a joint
venture focussing on clean energy and carbon credits.  The venture will be equipped to become the leader in the
Chinese carbon market, according to  a statement  on the website
of Mercuria.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mathew Carr in London at 
 m.carr@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alessandro Vitelli at 
 avitelli1@bloomberg.net  